# E2E Tests Directory

Place end-to-end test files here following the naming convention:
- `*.spec.ts` for Playwright tests

Example structure:
```
tests/e2e/
  auth/
    login.spec.ts
    logout.spec.ts
    register.spec.ts
  messaging/
    send-message.spec.ts
    receive-message.spec.ts
    message-history.spec.ts
  rooms/
    create-room.spec.ts
    join-room.spec.ts
    room-settings.spec.ts
  accessibility/
    keyboard-navigation.spec.ts
    screen-reader.spec.ts
  performance/
    page-load.spec.ts
    message-latency.spec.ts
  visual/
    chat-room.spec.ts
    login-page.spec.ts
  global-setup.ts
  global-teardown.ts
  fixtures/
    test-user.ts
  __snapshots__/
```

Run with: `npm run test:e2e`
Run with UI: `npm run test:e2e:ui`
Debug: `PWDEBUG=1 npm run test:e2e`
